    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1911-02-01T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1911-02-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="441"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d441">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 741.8215/37.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Chargé d’Affaires at
                            London</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-02-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 1, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 1569.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to inclose herewith a copy of a
                        note<hi rend="superscript">1</hi> which I have received from the foreign
                    office, dated the 31st ultimo, stating that Sir Edward Grey is informed by the
                    British consul general at Monrovia that the Sierra Leone-Liberia frontier
                    agreement has been ratified by the Government of Liberia. Sir E. Grey also
                    expresses <pb facs="0424" n="342" xml:id="pg_342"/> thanks for the action taken
                    by this embassy and by the Department in facilitating the settlement of the
                    question.</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">William Phillips.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
